title: CodeRunner 1.3.1
description:
CodeRunner text editor and compiler purchased from the Mac App Store. Perfect for PHP development without the need to run a PHP/MySQL server.




"Edit and run code in any programming language with just a single click. With CodeRunner, it has never been easier to write and test code, run scripts, work with algorithms, or simply experiment with a new coding or scripting language. Run code in AppleScript, C, C++, Java, JavaScript (Node.js), Lua, Objective-C, Perl, PHP, Python, Ruby, Shell or any other language you've installed on your system."
